As a Digital Ambassador, I designed a high-impact visual resource using Canva to educate peers on essential online safety. 
The infographic focuses on three critical pillars: 
Digital IQ for information credibility, 
Virtual Vaults for multi-factor authentication, 
and Professional Netiquette for effective communication. 
By condensing complex security topics into actionable tips, 
this resource empowers students to move from passive content consumption to becoming secure, creative digital builders.
